title: Vote of No Confidence
subtitle: Our coalition partners call for our removal
new-page: true
view-if: CHP_in_government = 1 and (in_weimar_coalition = 1 or in_grand_coalition = 1 or in_popular_front = 1) and coalition_dissent >= 3 and chp_votes < 50 and not constructive_vonc
tags: event
on-arrival: coalition_dissent = 2 if coalition_dissent > 2
go-to: vonc_menu

= Vote of No Confidence

Our coalition partners have called for a vote of no confidence against us. If this succeeds, there will be new elections.

@vonc_menu

- @let_it_happen: Accept the vote.

@let_it_happen
on-arrival: {!
    Q.CHP_in_government = 0;
    Q.in_weimar_coalition = 0;
    Q.in_grand_coalition = 0;
    Q.in_popular_front = 0;
    Q.coalition_dissent = 0;
    Q.next_election_time = Q.time + 3;
    Q.next_election_month = Q.month + 3;
    Q.next_election_year = Q.year;
    if (Q.next_election_month > 12) {
        Q.next_election_year += 1;
        Q.next_election_month -= 12;
    }
    Q.foreign_minister_party = "I";
    Q.interior_minister_party = "I";
    Q.justice_minister_party = "I";
    Q.labor_minister_party = "I";
    Q.economic_minister_party = "I";
    Q.finance_minister_party = "I";
    Q.agriculture_minister_party = "I";
    Q.education_minister_party = "I";
    Q.trade_minister_party = "I";
    Q.industrial_minister_party = "I";
!}

The vote succeeds and our government falls. New elections will be held soon.

New elections have been set for [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +].
